title: Raja Mariyadhai
subTitle: Raghuram, working for an authoritarian man Rajasekar, attempts to conceal his marriage as his boss is opposed to the concept of marriage.

title: Rasigan
subTitle: Vijay and Anitha fall head over heels in love with each other, but are are unable to express their feelings. When Anitha's father gets a wind of it, he tries separating the couple.

title: Thottu Paar
subTitle: Maharaja collaborates with a police officer to bail out minor offenders. Their actions take an unexpected turn when they assist a gangster who later assassinates a minister.

title: Vallal

title: Pudhu Nellu Pudhu Nathu
subTitle: An old widow returns to her village with her two sons. The elder son is an illiterate peasant, the younger an educated, urbane youth, who falls in love with an iron-fisted local landlord's daughter.
